title: Newt Jingrik Tweed about the November attack in San Bernardino
subtitle: It's almost certain that Newt Jingerick wasn't referring to San Bernardino being shot in a tweet on November 13, 2015.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: Newt Gingerick has been quoted for shooting on December 2, 2015 in San Bernardino on November 13, 2015.
